Package: rversioncontrol
Title: R Version Control and Cloud Connectivity Tutorial
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Contrino", email = "benjamin.contrino@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tutorial package demonstrating R project structure, version control 
    with renv, and cloud database connectivity using .env files. Covers SQL Server,
    Azure Blob Storage, Microsoft Fabric, Databricks, and Snowflake connections.
